# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.2.7] - 2024-09-19

### Bug Fixes

- Cfg flag usage for nightly detection
- Docs lint for link to stackoverflow

## [0.2.6] - 2024-01-31

### Bug Fixes

- Timeout usage

### Features

- Add inner(), inner_mut(), Deref/DerefMut impls
- Remove static requirement by using async-scoped
- Add no-default-bound feature

## [0.2.5] - 2023-10-20

### Bug Fixes

- Lint

### Refactor

- Lint cargo.toml w/ taplo

## [0.2.4] - 2023-10-16

### Bug Fixes

- Use of `cargo get`
- Clippy lints
- Add tokio time dep
- Tokio deps

### Miscellaneous Tasks

- Update deps

## [0.2.3] - 2023-08-09

### Bug Fixes

